location.fullValue: Aura Plan, Trinity Creek - The Retreat

data.description: Beautiful home in stunning Lochridge! Chef's delight kitchen w/ SS, Quartz Counters, Large Pantry, Massive Island w/Seating, and an oversized Breakfast Area. 1st flr Office with French Doors and soaring ceilings. Main flr owner's suite w/ vaulted Ceiling, Walk-in Closet w/ Custom Shelves & Cabinets. Main flr laundry. 2nd Fl w/ Loft, Media Room, Two Bedrooms w/ connecting full bath, and a 3rd Bedroom w/ ensuite Bath.  Amazing backyard that's cleared and ready for a pool or outdoor extravaganza of your choice! Walk across the street to the community pool; minutes to shopping, restaurants, entertainment, Harris Lake Park, Ting Park, DT Holly Springs, DT Fuquay, US-1, Hwy 55, and I-540!
